Module net.automatalib.api
Package net.automatalib.alphabet

Interface ProceduralOutputAlphabet<O>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - output symbol type
    All Superinterfaces:
    Alphabet<O>, ArrayWritable<O>, Collection<O>, Comparator<O>, IntFunction<O>, Iterable<O>, ToIntFunction<O>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultProceduralOutputAlphabet
    public interface ProceduralOutputAlphabet<O>
extends Alphabet<O>
    A specialized Alphabet for procedural systems that combines a regular output alphabet with a designated error symbol.
